        "content": "## SETUP REQUIRED\n\nGoogle Sheets Structure:\nSheet: \"Invoices\"\n‚Ä¢ Column A: Invoice Number  \n‚Ä¢ Column B: Invoice Date  \n‚Ä¢ Column C: Due Date  \n‚Ä¢ Column D: Vendor Name  \n‚Ä¢ Column E: Total Amount  \n‚Ä¢ Column F: Currency  \n‚Ä¢ Column G: Items  \n‚Ä¢ Column H: Tax  \n‚Ä¢ Column I: Category  \n‚Ä¢ Column J: Approved\n‚Ä¢ Column K: Approval Notes\n‚Ä¢ Column L: Reviewed By\n\nRequired Credentials:\n‚Ä¢ Google Drive Credential  \n‚Ä¢ Gmail Credential \n‚Ä¢ Google Sheets Credential \n‚Ä¢ OpenAI API Key (GPT-4)\n"
