    {
      "id": "3d3cd92a-9ea7-4a4f-a9b5-aae689f719e5",
      "name": "Sticky Note1",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        1320,
        -60
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "width": 480,
        "height": 2240,
        "content": "# üîç LinkedIn Jobs API ‚Äì Parameter Guide\n\nUse this object to query LinkedIn job listings.  \nEach field lets you filter results based on different criteria.\n\n```json\n{\n  \"location\": \"{{ $json.Location }}\",\n  \"keyword\": \"{{ $json.Keyword }}\",\n  \"country\": \"{{ $json.Country }}\",\n  \"time_range\": \"Past 24 hours\",\n  \"job_type\": \"Part-time\",\n  \"experience_level\": \"\",\n  \"remote\": \"\",\n  \"company\": \"\"\n}\n```\n\n## üßæ Field Explanations & Valid Options\n\n### üó∫Ô∏è location\nCity or region where the job is located.\nUse a city or region name.\n‚úÖ Example: \"Berlin\", \"New York\"\n\n### üß† keyword\nJob title or search keywords.\nUse terms like role names or skills.\n‚úÖ Example: \"Data Scientist\", \"Growth Marketing\"\n\n### üåç country\nCountry code in ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 format.\n‚úÖ Example: \"US\", \"DE\", \"IL\"\n\n### ‚è±Ô∏è time_range\nPosting date filter.\nLimits results based on how recently jobs were posted.\nAccepted values:\n- Any Time\n- Past 24 hours\n- Past Week\n- Past Month\n‚úÖ Example: \"Past Week\"\n\n### üíº job_type\nType of employment.\nUse a single value or comma-separated list.\nAccepted values:\n- Full-time\n- Part-time\n- Contract\n- Temporary\n- Internship\n- Volunteer\n- Other\n‚úÖ Example: \"Full-time,Contract\"\n\n### üéØ experience_level\nSeniority level of the job.\nAccepted values:\n- Internship\n- Entry level\n- Associate\n- Mid-Senior level\n- Director\n- Executive\n‚úÖ Example: \"Mid-Senior level\"\n\n### üåê remote\nWorkplace type.\nAccepted values:\n- Remote\n- On-site\n- Hybrid\n- (leave blank for no preference)\n‚úÖ Example: \"Remote\"\n\n### üè¢ company\nFilter by company name.\nOptional. Use plain text.\n‚úÖ Example: \"Google\", \"Spotify\"\n\n## ‚úÖ Full Example\n\n```json\n{\n  \"location\": \"New York\",\n  \"keyword\": \"UI Designer\",\n  \"country\": \"US\",\n  \"time_range\": \"Past Week\",\n  \"job_type\": \"Full-time,Contract\",\n  \"experience_level\": \"Mid-Senior level\",\n  \"remote\": \"Hybrid\",\n  \"company\": \"Spotify\"\n}\n```\n\n"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
